{"tid":1636734,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我係由深黃變淺黃，再到中立。再咁落去我地會輸。","createTime":"2019-10-07T20:14:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T05:12:14.000Z","uid":291185,"like":12,"dislike":154,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"d4451b483e817df2b01d1ca248cb9457c8f87c45","tid":1636734,"uid":291185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T20:14:04.000Z","msg":"四個月啦，我地得到啲咩？<br />\n2000幾個手足被補<br />\n數以百計受傷數字<br />\n幾多隻眼，幾多對腳，幾多人中彈，幾多人死？<br />\n到宜家，我地得到啲咩？<br />\n我地曾經佔過上風 曾經有200萬同路人上街<br />\n得到外國關注 林鄭都動議撤回送中條例<br />\n<br />\n但到今日 <br />\n我見到嘅係身邊嘅深黃開始改口 <br />\n話唔應該搞裝修、搞公交 影響民眾<br />\n其實搞呢啲對我地黎講真係百害而無一利<br />\n搞到本身中立嘅人轉淺藍<br />\n特別係嗰啲出去搵食嘅人 因為交通令到佢哋冇飯開<br />\n因為鋪頭閂晒，因為地鐵唔開令到佢哋嘅唔方便<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講，老一輩嘅人本身就覺得生活飽足，<br />\n餐餐有飯開就OK，冇咩事唔好搞到佢哋<br />\n自由民主呢啲野對佢哋來講係bonus<br />\n但係當你影響到佢哋最基本嘅需求，<br />\n佢哋當然唔支持啦<br />\n我地需要民心 需要人數支持<br />\n唔可以再令佢地轉向<br />\n<br />\n咁耐以來 有邊次搞地鐵，搞中資鋪頭<br />\n會換來市民正面嘅回應<br />\n冇 咁不如真係對準政權<br />\n<br />\n不論係和理非 前線勇武 文宣<br />\n係一直以來都付出左好多<br />\n唔可以就咁就輸<br />\n我哋要檢討 再搵一個出路<br />\n<br />\n天琦都講過<br />\n「你們或許因而心中充滿憤怒，這乃是人之常情。但我懇請你們不要被仇恨支配自己，在危難中，仍要時刻保持警覺與思考。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港  時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"18527e4ea6ee61af803d9526170f795b432ce592","tid":1636734,"uid":233873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T20:14:35.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"eb6854b9a308bc759647f8d23c900df7849c293f","tid":1636734,"uid":104296,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T20:15:18.000Z","msg":"又係五毛"},{"pid":"5e2e82c6d931f4abb59efbb1e6efd8c8825253ac","tid":1636734,"uid":166594,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T20:16:09.000Z","msg":"早D抖咪上嚟呃兩餐啦五毛"},{"pid":"7095dfe734defb160bb49d182b605f2251f569ba","tid":1636734,"uid":161709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T20:16:36.000Z","msg":"垃圾五毛"},{"pid":"d50353400f54cb4e57e6bf8d7a68102829b8b7f3","tid":1636734,"uid":28960,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T20:17:23.000Z","msg":"After this 4 months, you still can change from yellow to blue, you definately have brain problem<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5782a20652e4fbf99b1b38ea75a9bea47c3804","tid":1636734,"uid":230239,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T20:18:40.000Z","msg":"建議樓主唔好再喺連登晒氣<br />\n呢度已經畀人滲透曬<br />\n冇得救"},{"pid":"0f6b0ea3e2b078a937897d68bf8953473bbbc396","tid":1636734,"uid":293667,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T20:19:35.000Z","msg":"係深黃就知唔會割啦 傻系"},{"pid":"f008562bffc0a8345144f8a9feae417aea3b93bb","tid":1636734,"uid":319380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T20:19:54.000Z","msg":"罐頭文章，無內涵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"469413908e03dc38b8e2faa0e2ba0360435160a5","tid":1636734,"uid":36207,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T20:20:44.000Z","msg":"請問公交係邊個地方嘅用語"},{"pid":"62ea97f7027a198d333c1a32915ae1ad73c95c2a","tid":1636734,"uid":24737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T20:21:27.000Z","msg":"中立學人咩人講光復香港 <br />\n死撚開啦"},{"pid":"0176931b5e769f00927aedce0c52a3d8418eb6ae","tid":1636734,"uid":139322,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T20:21:45.000Z","msg":"係深黃見到班狗,林鄭咁多個月所作所為又點會變淺變中立呀"},{"pid":"44b50827ff8a8a732c8380987ebed6a7c11531ab","tid":1636734,"uid":44870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T20:21:58.000Z","msg":"新5毛confirmed , banned"},{"pid":"9bfa925eb2b8f575a4c41d66e59d048bee92b052","tid":1636734,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T20:21:59.000Z","msg":"拉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n深黃但第二個po<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 呢度全部冷氣撚黎..."},{"pid":"8ee0decef03738631e0000bbe5586eb5278b3b61","tid":1636734,"uid":14087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"